title: NVIDIA Graphics Card: Fan speed
agents: linux, windows
catalog: os/hardware
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the fan speed of an NVIDIA graphics card
 using the command line tool {nvidia-smi}.
 The check only works if that tool is installed.

 You can configure upper levels for fan speed.

item:
 PCI bus ID of the graphics card

discovery:
 One service is created for each available graphics card if fan speed
 is available.
